## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The lack of specific data or recent studies in some sources may limit the depth of analysis. Additionally, the subjective nature of health priorities can vary based on individual circumstances and cultural contexts. Further research, including empirical studies, could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.

